{"tid":869192,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"★ 傳渣打公布季績時宣佈裁員最多300人　同時凍結部分招聘","createTime":"2018-10-20T07:13:42.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-21T11:58:41.000Z","uid":19454,"like":14,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"c95f70fc33a5d15d67c2b8428a03534a056c9aad","tid":869192,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T07:13:42.000Z","msg":"據英國《金融時報》引述消息人士報道，渣打集團（2888）正準備新一輪裁員，以降低成本及回應投資者對業績的憂慮。<br />\n<br />\n消息人士指，裁員行動將於本月稍後宣布第3季業績時公布。該行計劃於中東和非洲裁員最多300人；另一名消息人士稱，渣打將凍結部分招聘，和限制員工「出差」時開支以削減成本。<br />\n<br />\n渣打發言人回應時稱，該行早前已表示下半年的開支將與上半年相若，現時仍維持此看法。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/財經快訊/249102/傳渣打公布季績時宣佈裁員最多300人-同時凍結部分招聘\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%E8%B2%A1%E7%B6%93%E5%BF%AB%E8%A8%8A%2F249102%2F%E5%82%B3%E6%B8%A3%E6%89%93%E5%85%AC%E5%B8%83%E5%AD%A3%E7%B8%BE%E6%99%82%E5%AE%A3%E4%BD%88%E8%A3%81%E5%93%A1%E6%9C%80%E5%A4%9A300%E4%BA%BA-%E5%90%8C%E6%99%82%E5%87%8D%E7%B5%90%E9%83%A8%E5%88%86%E6%8B%9B%E8%81%98&d=x9x9j%2BX2LrZFnyqQCHj1Sdr9upuAghWR75VkZoMWgf8%3D&h=fb58c396\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/財經快訊/249102/傳渣打公布季績時宣佈裁員最多300人-同時凍結部分招聘</a>"},{"pid":"d00dff1aee2ec7cd11668f340c2681179689316c","tid":869192,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T07:13:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bb964aaab5cd792177b21cc65770696e6004e0e","tid":869192,"uid":19454,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T07:14:28.000Z","msg":"香港肯定超過300<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1a820ef270e56222cce95daef5d6ed30f743dfa9","tid":869192,"uid":19454,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-20T07:15:13.000Z","msg":"港